---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service | Thryv Marketing Solutions"
  description="Terms of service for Thryv Marketing Solutions."
  canonical="https://thryvmarketingsolutions.com/terms/"
>
<nav>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <a href="/" class="nav-logo"><img src="/logos/logo-trimmed.png" alt="Thryv Marketing Solutions" /></a>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="/#services">Services</a></li>
        <li><a href="/#pricing">Pricing</a></li>
        <li><a href="/#contact">Contact</a></li>
      </ul>
      <div class="nav-cta">
        <a href="/#contact" class="btn btn-blue">Get Free Audit</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>
<main style="max-width:760px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px 24px;">
  <h1 style="font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,40px);font-weight:800;color:var(--dark);margin-bottom:8px;">Terms of Service</h1>
  <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--gray);margin-bottom:48px;">Last updated: May 1, 2026</p>

  <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:32px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;color:var(--gray);">
    <section>
      <h2 style="font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:var(--dark);margin-bottom:12px;">Services</h2>
      <p>Thryv Marketing Solutions provides digital marketing services including local SEO, Google Business Profile management, reputation management, paid advertising, website design, and AI automation on a month-to-month basis. All services are billed monthly with no long-term contracts. Either party may terminate services with 30 days written notice.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2 style="font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:var(--dark);margin-bottom:12px;">Payment</h2>
      <p>Services are billed monthly in advance. Payment is due within 7 days of invoice. Thryv Marketing Solutions reserves the right to pause services on accounts more than 14 days past due.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2 style="font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:var(--dark);margin-bottom:12px;">Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>Content, strategies, and reports produced for a client are owned by that client upon full payment. Thryv Marketing Solutions retains the right to use anonymized performance data for internal research and marketing purposes.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2 style="font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:var(--dark);margin-bottom:12px;">Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>Thryv Marketing Solutions does not guarantee specific ranking positions, review counts, or revenue outcomes. Marketing results depend on factors outside our control including algorithm changes, market conditions, and client responsiveness.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2 style="font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:var(--dark);margin-bottom:12px;">Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about these terms: <a href="mailto:hello@thryvmarketingsolutions.com" style="color:var(--blue);font-weight:600;">hello@thryvmarketingsolutions.com</a></p>
    </section>
  </div>
</main>
<footer>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="footer-bottom" style="padding:32px 0;">
      <p>© 2026 Thryv Marketing Solutions. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p class="hablamos">Hablamos Español</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
</BaseLayout>
